Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.31,0:00:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometime ago, for the sake of living, we left behind our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.27,0:00:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We deceived ourselves, clinging to this mere illusion as we danced...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.57,0:00:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With closed eyes, at the end of the horizon,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.83,0:00:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was searching for your smiling face...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.29,0:00:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We embrace our dreams and continue on...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.30,0:00:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}within the swaying traces of memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.23,0:01:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday, I will once again grasp hold of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.32,0:01:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}these feelings I have locked away in my heart... Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.59,0:01:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After losing the fight with Rafael, Yugi's soul has been taken from the other Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.59,0:01:40.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know exactly how you feel, but now's not the time to be feeling sorry for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.35,0:01:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's go find the secrets of Doma and get back our lost souls!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.44,0:01:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But Haga and Ryuzaki going missing like that's bothering me...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.96,0:01:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You don't think...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.46,0:01:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...they joined forces with Doma?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.96,0:02:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Runaway Train Duel"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.81,0:02:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, we're off now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.66,0:02:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of Professor Hopkins and Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.25,0:02:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Just leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.12,0:02:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as the professor recovers, we'll catch up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.21,0:02:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're really counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.34,0:02:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do a thing without the professor, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.51,0:02:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.05,0:02:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to save Darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.14,0:02:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Calm down, Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.55,0:02:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come on...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.68,0:02:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.31,0:02:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi-{\i0}kun{\i1} is the one suffering the most here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.28,0:02:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're an idiot, Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.17,0:02:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.46,0:02:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.46,0:02:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.55,0:02:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.51,0:03:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.33,0:03:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.54,0:03:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Yugi, take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.55,0:03:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it beautiful?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.22,0:03:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what we'll see in Florida!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.34,0:03:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh~! I should've brought a swimsuit with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.81,0:03:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you hungry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.23,0:03:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we go find the dining cart?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.07,0:04:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheer up already, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're feeling down,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.42,0:04:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you can't just keep feeling sorry for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.51,0:04:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll all think of a way to get the other Yugi back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.47,0:04:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.27,0:04:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.77,0:04:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.24,0:04:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no use talking to him right now, Anzu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.03,0:04:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only one on his mind right now is usual Yugi, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.73,0:04:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let him be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.62,0:05:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, the great Katsuya Jounouchi,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will save the other Yugi no matter what it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.92,0:05:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.14,0:05:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Back then, I couldn't stop myself from being consumed by the darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.31,0:05:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I lost myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's about time we settled this, Rafael.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.67,0:05:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I use Black Magician Girl as a sacrifice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Eat {\b0}this{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.66,0:05:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And as a result...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't stare at me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.90,0:05:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't stare at me with those eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}O Nameless Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bear the wrath of these Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Guardian Eatos attacks!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gospel of Truth!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.22,0:06:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.18,0:06:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.16,0:06:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I lost something I cherished more than my own life...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.09,0:06:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.26,0:06:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi hasn't come back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.14,0:06:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, isn't this a bit strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.48,0:06:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.79,0:06:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi was the only one who got up and left this entire time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.98,0:06:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just when did everyone in the entire train disappear without a trace?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.81,0:07:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one up here either!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.56,0:07:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the next train?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.28,0:07:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.45,0:07:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's up with this train!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.83,0:07:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone just disappeared without a trace when we weren't looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.96,0:07:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't even reached the first stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.38,0:07:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way something like this could happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.92,0:07:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be {\i1}their{\i0} doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.10,0:07:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.19,0:08:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.24,0:08:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.20,0:08:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.58,0:08:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.58,0:08:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.12,0:08:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.71,0:08:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.79,0:08:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try and contact another train!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.75,0:08:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.80,0:08:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.97,0:08:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.97,0:08:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this really {\i1}was{\i0} Doma's doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.60,0:08:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.69,0:08:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.11,0:08:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.15,0:08:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dinosaur Ryuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.07,0:08:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:08:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.30,0:09:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go scaring us like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi... I got some business to take care a' with ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.29,0:09:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Business with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.46,0:09:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came ta' take away that soul a' yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.13,0:09:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is anyone there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.72,0:09:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please stop the train right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.64,0:09:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mr. Driver!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.01,0:09:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someone please stop the train!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.77,0:09:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there no driver on this train at all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.36,0:09:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.11,0:09:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to check the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.66,0:09:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.83,0:09:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Insector Haga!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.05,0:09:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haga?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.88,0:09:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he doing here of all places?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.55,0:10:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, Duel with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.76,0:10:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haga, you aren't telling me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me warn you in advance. I'm no longer the same as I was before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.28,0:10:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's one of Doma's now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.62,0:10:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki, are you tryin' to tell me...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.98,0:10:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.27,0:10:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you join up with Doma?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.23,0:10:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, it's to beat {\i1}you{\i0}, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.69,0:10:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haga...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.99,0:10:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a match, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.11,0:10:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.16,0:10:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.78,0:10:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too dangerous up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.11,0:11:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haga, do you even know what you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.86,0:11:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you guys have a Duel like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.95,0:11:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, she's scary~!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.28,0:11:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl like you is much cuter when she keeps her mouth shut!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.87,0:11:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that mean!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.29,0:11:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bad, but you aren't the one I'm after.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.92,0:11:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's {\i1}you{\i0}, Nameless Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.96,0:11:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.05,0:11:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.38,0:11:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That you have two personalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.97,0:11:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.76,0:11:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the other Yugi is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.98,0:11:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.10,0:11:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna know so badly,\Nyou're gonna have to Duel me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.59,0:11:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you if you can beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.32,0:11:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haga!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.40,0:11:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.70,0:11:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now let's fight, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.62,0:11:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.41,0:11:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.33,0:11:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.16,0:11:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you guys are the one who screwed with the train, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.63,0:11:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you trying to pull here!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.34,0:12:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Yugi and Anzu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.25,0:12:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.42,0:12:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi's bein' taken care a' by that Haga freak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.59,0:12:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Haga "freak" joined Doma?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.68,0:12:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.47,0:12:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's not just Ryuzaki, but even Haga?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.64,0:12:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi, I got a huge score to settle with ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.90,0:12:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time we finished this once and for all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.26,0:12:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't freaking kid around with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.40,0:12:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you two have any clue what joining up with Doma even means?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.70,0:12:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're trying to destroy the world, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.45,0:12:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.74,0:12:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That ain't got a {\i1}thing{\i0} to do with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.29,0:12:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm cool long as I beat ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,0:12:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now get in position!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.21,0:12:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You givin' me no choice here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.04,0:12:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's forget this idiot and go find Yugi and Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.13,0:12:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.84,0:12:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ain't gettin' away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.97,0:12:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm serious here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.26,0:12:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.34,0:12:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.43,0:12:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get this party started!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.89,0:12:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Barrier of Orichalcos...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.89,0:12:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit it, Ryuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.48,0:13:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you use that thing, the loser'll get his soul taken!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.65,0:13:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate The Barrier of Orichalcos.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.61,0:13:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.67,0:13:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.96,0:13:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Power's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Power's surgin' through me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.26,0:13:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki! You dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.80,0:13:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.01,0:13:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Ryuzaki ass is really able to use that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.52,0:13:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now no one's able to get out of that barrier until a winner is decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.98,0:13:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the loser...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.44,0:13:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya lil' bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.69,0:13:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told ya I was serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.90,0:13:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.36,0:13:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,YOU STUPID ASS!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.04,0:13:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.96,0:14:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand back, Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.63,0:14:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.92,0:14:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But the way you are now,\N you shouldn't be Dueling against anyone...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.34,0:14:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.30,0:14:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.26,0:14:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll start things off by playing this card!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.10,0:14:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Barrier of Orichalcos...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.14,0:14:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don'tcha tell me, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.23,0:14:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's it feel like to play this card?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.44,0:14:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it feel good to have your body and soul completely consumed by the darkness of your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.99,0:14:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just jokin' with ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.74,0:14:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me such a scary look, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.75,0:14:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find out this very moment when I play it myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.69,0:14:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.79,0:14:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know what will happen to you if you play that card?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.38,0:14:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm using it {\i1}because{\i0} I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.93,0:14:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.11,0:15:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.69,0:15:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.62,0:15:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.20,0:15:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is the power of Orichalcos!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.42,0:15:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it has begun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.75,0:15:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though it's true we don't know how those two will fair,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.22,0:15:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it'll be good if they can win the Duels and make the Pharaoh's soul ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.64,0:15:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if they are to lose, we get their souls instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.85,0:15:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just you wait, Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.65,0:15:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll save you no matter what it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.40,0:15:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, Pheromone Wasp!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.45,0:15:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And because of Orichalcos Barrier's effect,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.53,0:16:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pheromone Wasp's Attack goes up by 500 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.37,0:16:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also set two reverse cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.71,0:16:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.29,0:16:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.79,0:16:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.75,0:16:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Retrained Elf Swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.09,0:16:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go, Haga!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.43,0:16:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Haga has two reverse cards on the field...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.56,0:16:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be reckless, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.48,0:16:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Retrained Elf Swordsman, attack Pheromone Wasp!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.44,0:16:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse Card open!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.61,0:16:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Trap Card Mimesis!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.16,0:16:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mimesis{\r}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.45,0:16:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.24,0:16:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When an Insect-Type Monster on the field is attacked,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.95,0:16:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can replace it with any other Level Four Monster from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.21,0:16:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By Mimesis's effect,\N I return Pheromone Wasp to my hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.79,0:16:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and Special Summon Parasite Caterpillar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.22,0:16:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It switched with Parasite Caterpillar!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.68,0:17:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fell for it, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.27,0:17:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Parasite Caterpillar, I mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.14,0:17:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Infect the opposing Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This allots for a great, {\i1}great{\i0} amount of torment!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.45,0:17:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi, now your life's on the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.37,0:17:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're a Duelist, fight me head on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.62,0:17:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.71,0:17:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.83,0:17:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't say anything else!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.50,0:17:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take this Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.29,0:17:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.80,0:17:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange, I'll be coming at you full force!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.59,0:17:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.55,0:17:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn right ya are!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.97,0:17:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd be a retard ta' be holdin' back!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.26,0:17:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Isn't a Duel to beat Ryuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.02,0:17:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a Duel to {\b0}save{\b1} Ryuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.98,0:17:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.10,0:17:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Special Summon Fleet-Footed Gilasaurus!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.11,0:17:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.07,0:17:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Special Summoned?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.57,0:18:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.36,0:18:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya see, this guy's a Monster that gets treated as a Special Summon when ya Summon 'im.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.00,0:18:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I Special Summon {\i1}another{\i0} Fleet-Footed Gilasaurus!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.67,0:18:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Another{\i0} Special Summon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.29,0:18:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.88,0:18:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.46,0:18:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Chitoptera!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.88,0:18:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.05,0:18:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He Summoned three Monsters in just one turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.64,0:18:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, their Attack goes up 500 points cuz a the Orichalcos Seal's effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.10,0:18:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To have a Monster with a Special Effect that lets you Summon three from your hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're one freakin' lucky bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.28,0:18:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.07,0:18:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't {\i1}you{\i0} the one that's always dependin' on luck in your Duels?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.99,0:18:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gah! What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.70,0:18:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.62,0:18:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda, you {\i1}ass{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.16,0:18:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose side are you on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.70,0:18:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mah bad, dude!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.37,0:18:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.54,0:18:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll place one final reverse card,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.42,0:18:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.51,0:18:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.46,0:18:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.26,0:19:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He Summoned three Monsters with 1900 Attack Points right off the bat...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.22,0:19:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shit...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.68,0:19:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Jet Black Soldier - Panther Warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He can't attack unless I sacrifice a Monster first,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.65,0:19:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but his Attack Points far exceed theirs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.98,0:19:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if I can't attack, he's in the same boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.28,0:19:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Scapegoat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.74,0:19:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll also play a Set Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.28,0:19:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.62,0:19:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.91,0:19:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.04,0:19:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll Summon this guy again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.33,0:19:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pheromone Wasp!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.46,0:19:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just have one on my field, Retrained Elf Swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.67,0:19:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But because he was poisoned by Poison Caterpillar, he can neither attack nor defend against the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.60,0:19:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.56,0:19:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Direct Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.94,0:19:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.65,0:20:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Pheromone Wasp successfully directly attacks the enemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.36,0:20:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at the end of the Battle Phase,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.41,0:20:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can Special Summon a Level Four or lower Insect-Type Monster from my Deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.08,0:20:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to Pheromone Wasp's Special Effect,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.75,0:20:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Special Summon Leghul!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.13,0:20:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And furthermore, the Continuous Magic Card, Insecticide Barrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.34,0:20:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.51,0:20:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I activate this, all Insect-Type Monsters are unable to attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.69,0:20:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Yugi doesn't have any Insect-Type Monsters on the field...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.86,0:20:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any Monster you hold that is infected...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.32,0:20:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will evolve into its true form, Poison Butterfly, on the third turn of its being infected!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.37,0:20:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.91,0:20:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And at the end of each of your turns,\N you lose 500 of your Life Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.54,0:21:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Poison Butterfly has 2700 Attack Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.34,0:21:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were to attack me with {\i1}that{\i0},\N I wouldn't stand a {\i1}chance{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.76,0:21:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could almost say I'm giving you a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.64,0:21:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.06,0:21:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Insector Haga...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.81,0:21:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no doubt he's much stronger than before...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.73,0:21:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So this is the power of the Orichalcos...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait for me, Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.73,0:21:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to save you no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.90,0:21:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.95,0:21:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.10,0:22:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The houses lined down the street drifting by being dyed red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.46,0:22:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I notice pain, it'll turn into happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.07,0:22:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time people wipe away tears, they understand bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.14,0:22:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The warm strength that you gave me will change into kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.62,0:22:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Overflowing feelings don't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.90,0:22:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll live while I feel it, for me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.80,0:22:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Healed by overflowing friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.95,0:23:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our fated encounter is a truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.47,0:23:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and someday we'll be able to understand each other
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.33,0:23:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Atop the runaway train, Yugi faces off against Insector Haga.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.92,0:23:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And back where we left them, Jounouchi is challenged to a Duel by Dinosaur Ryuzaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.01,0:23:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With help from Doma, both of their decks have been powered up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.76,0:23:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They push Yugi and Jounouchi into a corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.22,0:23:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi's in no state to be Dueling intelligently right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.18,0:23:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.64,0:23:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let Haga confuse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.27,0:23:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.98,0:23:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Powered Up Decks!\N Haga and Ryuzaki"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.73,0:23:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!

